5.) Set up static IP's (for machines with them)
- edit /etc/network/interfaces, and add lines like:
auto iface eth0 inet static
	address 192.168.9.1
        netmask 255.255.255.0
	gateway 192.168.9.254

ifdown eth0
ifup eth0

